ContentDesc_Rabanastre: Recently, residents of Kugane woke to find hovering above their city an airship unlike any ever seen. Yet while of Garlean design, the vessel distinctly lacked the bleak outfitting common in the Empire's warmachina. No, this was the Prima Vista, private stage for the Majestic Imperial Theater Company─a troupe having won acclaim across Garlemald for their timeless work, The Zodiac Brave Story. Which begets the question...why are they here? The answer to that question and more lies in the selfsame legend of which they sing. The legend of Ivalice.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18011_Text: You do not fear me!? You will!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18012_Text: Fools! You have not...yet seen...the limit of my reach...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18013_Text: Without order, creation is doomed to descend into chaos. I bring that order. You will kneel.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18015_Text: Hark! What army marches on Rofocale's demesne?
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18016_Text: Ah... To die a good death...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18017_Text: It is to be a fight, then? I am only too happy to oblige!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18018_Text: Fool is the dog who bares his teeth before his master!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18020_Text: You are but blood to stain the circle!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18021_Text: The gods have no eyes for chattel!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18023_Text: The world has no place for such wretches. Your claim to life is forfeit!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18024_Text: I am the truth from which you run!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18025_Text: I am the lies upon which you sup!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18028_Text: Does it grieve you to see the depths of your own weakness laid bare? Maggots...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18029_Text: You do not belong in my world. Step into Nothing!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18030_Text: Sound the battle horns! Soldiers, to me!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18031_Text: The heavens tremble in my wake!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18032_Text: The auracite! Gaze upon its undying brilliance and know true fear!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18033_Text: Hah hah hah hah! Even a hound knows when to turn tail! Would you have us think you less than chattel!?
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18034_Text: Ill fortune befall all who dare gaze upon me!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18035_Text: An inescapable hell awaits you all!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18036_Text: Without light, there can be only darkness!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18037_Text: Born of darkness, born of night! Come forth, my children!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18038_Text: To maintain order, one must first have control.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18039_Text: The land seeks order. It will not suffer the chaos you peddle. Nor will I!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18041_Text: Resistance will be met with retribution! The land shall bury your screams!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18042_Text: To defy order is to defy creation itself!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18044_Text: Even the laws of life itself are mine to bend! Rise sand! Rise stone! Heed my bidding!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18045_Text: Come! The cleansing flame will seal all wounds!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18046_Text: Rise dark water, and grant me strength!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18047_Text: Goddess of ice, be my blade!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18048_Text: Goddess of ice, be my shield!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18049_Text: Living shield, protect me from evil!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18050_Text: Freeze, dark waters! Steel my body! Steel my resolve!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18051_Text: Let the ichor flow. Let it birth the mire that will drown mine enemies!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18056_Text: Before us lies the Royal City. My father is somewhere inside. I can feel it.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18058_Text: Something foul prevents our crossing. Ware its numbing breath!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18059_Text: Cid was not mistaken in his assessment of your skill in battle. Still, I worry that something even more sinister awaits us ahead.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18060_Text: Seeq bandits! It appears the deplorable creatures are here to raid abandoned homes.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18061_Text: My father mentioned the Empire using their might to put down rebellions within the city, but this destruction is too widespread. What if that creature we fought earlier...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18062_Text: More bandits...despite all the creatures we've encountered? I know not whether they are brave or foolish.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18063_Text: Another of the twisted “others”! This is not the work of the Empire. Something is wrong here.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18064_Text: Again, you have proven your worth to this expedition. Let us see what lies beneath the city.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18065_Text: Welcome to the Garamsythe Waterway. These tunnels are said to have existed since before even the Kingdom of Dalmasca was born. As the city grows, channels are widened, and new outlets dug. I would venture that some of the pools are so deep, no one alive has ever seen their bottoms.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18066_Text: The creatures here are not mere beasts or voidsent. The secrets that lie beyond must be ones worth keeping.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18067_Text: Any doubts I had of your participation in this rescue I have no longer. I was wrong to place mistrust in Cid and my sister's judgment. Now let us continue on. I sense we are close to our goal.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18068_Text: These ruins... We are no longer in Rabanastre, my friends. This is Lesalia. The Lesalia of Ivalician legend!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18069_Text: The air here feels...wrong. Can't you sense it? Death awaits us in yon chamber.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18071_Text: The ice burns hotter than flame! You are branded for life!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18072_Text: Crawl forth from the shadows, my pet!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18073_Text: Pah! You have yet to witness the auracite's true might!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18074_Text: I walk the shadows. You will not see me until my lance has transfixed your very soul!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_18075_Text: The tip of my lance is already at your necks. Submit, or die.
